```

### clip-path 绘制多边形
```css
/* 菱形 */
.diamond {
  clip-path: polygon(50% 0%, 100% 50%, 50% 100%, 0% 50%);
}

/* 六边形 */
.hexagon {
  clip-path: polygon(25% 0%, 75% 0%, 100% 50%, 75% 100%, 25% 100%, 0% 50%);
}

/* 星形 */
.star {
  clip-path: polygon(50% 0%, 61% 35%, 98% 35%, 68% 57%, 79% 91%, 50% 70%, 21% 91%, 32% 57%, 2% 35%, 39% 35%);
}
```

### CSS 绘制图标
```css
/* 汉堡菜单 */
.hamburger,
.hamburger::before,
.hamburger::after {
  display: block;
  width: 24px;
  height: 2px;
  background: currentColor;
}

.hamburger {
  position: relative;
}

.hamburger::before {
  content: '';
  position: absolute;
  top: -8px;
}

.hamburger::after {
  content: '';
  position: absolute;
  top: 8px;
}
```
